OL,3,CMan arrested after Winston Churchill
OL,4,Cstatue daubed with graffiti
OL,6,FA 38-year-old man has been arrested
OL,7,Fafter the statue of Sir Winston
OL,8,FChurchill in Westminster was defaced
OL,9,Fwith graffiti branding the former
OL,10,Fprime minister a "Zionist war
OL,11,Fcriminal".
OL,13,FOther phrases including "Stop the
OL,14,FGenocide" and "Free Palestine" were
OL,15,Fsprayed in red paint on the bronze
OL,16,Fsculpture in Parliament Square,
OL,17,FWestminster.
OL,19,FFurther graffiti read "Never again is
OL,20,FNow" and "Globalise the Intifada".
OL,26,@rD@ROUsD@IO]uD@YOUvD@IO]vD@OOUvD@^O]{D@
OL,26,AWOU|D@DO]|D@JOU|D@aO]
