OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1772460676
OL,3,CMan arrested after Winston Churchill
OL,4,Cstatue daubed with graffiti
OL,6,FA 38-year-old man has been arrested on
OL,7,Fsuspicion of racially aggravated
OL,8,Fcriminal damage and remains in custody.
OL,10,FThe Metropolitan Police said a man was
OL,11,Fseen spraying graffiti on the statue
OL,12,Fjust after 4am on Friday. According to
OL,13,Fthe force officers were on the scene
OL,14,Fwithin two minutes.
OL,16,FThe statue has been cordoned off and
OL,17,Fwas being cleaned on Friday morning.
OL,19,FDowning Street described the vandalism
OL,20,Fas "completely abhorrent".
OL,26,@|D@DOU|D@YO]
