CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1772460676
OL,3,CMan arrested after Winston Churchill
OL,4,Cstatue daubed with graffiti
OL,6,FA Number 10 spokesman said: "It's
OL,7,Fobviously a disgrace ... Churchill was
OL,8,Fa great Briton.
OL,10,F"This Government will always stand up
OL,11,Ffor our values and the perpetrator
OL,12,Fmust be held to account.
OL,14,F"We're glad the police have made an
OL,15,Farrest."
OL,17,FThe Campaign Against Antisemitism also
OL,18,Fcondemned the vandalism.
OL,26,@nD@]OUvD@AOUwD@HO]
