OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1772460676
OL,3,CMan arrested after Winston Churchill
OL,4,Cstatue daubed with graffiti
OL,6,FA spokesperson said: "The red triangle
OL,7,Fis a symbol used by Hamas over the
OL,8,Fpast several years to delineate
OL,9,Ftargets for violence and by activists
OL,10,Fworldwide to show solidarity with the
OL,11,Fterrorist group and support for its
OL,12,Fmethods and objectives.
OL,14,F"This vandalism underscores how vile
OL,15,Fand unpatriotic these extremists are.
OL,16,FThey don't just hate Jews: they hate
OL,17,FBritain."
OL,26,@nD@VOU
