OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1772460676
OL,3,CMan arrested after Winston Churchill
OL,4,Cstatue daubed with graffiti
OL,6,FLast December both the Metropolitan
OL,7,FPolice and Greater Manchester Police
OL,8,Fannounced anyone chanting the
OL,9,Fcontroversial slogan "globalise the
OL,10,Fintifada" would face arrest.
OL,12,FThe decision by the two police forces
OL,13,Fcame in the wake of the Bondi Beach
OL,14,Fterror attack, and the terror attack
OL,15,Fat Heaton Park synagogue in Manchester
OL,16,Fon October 2.
OL,18,FThe former prime minister's statue has
OL,19,Fbeen vandalised several times in the
OL,20,Fpast, including during protests.
OL,26,@qD@VOUrD@IO]
