PN,40706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1772460676
OL,3,CMan arrested after Winston Churchill
OL,4,Cstatue daubed with graffiti
OL,6,FIt was scrawled with graffiti accusing
OL,7,FSir Winston of being a racist in June
OL,8,F2020 during a Black Lives Matter
OL,9,Fprotest triggered by the death of
OL,10,FGeorge Floyd in the US.
OL,12,FLater that year, in October, an
OL,13,FExtinction Rebellion activist was
OL,14,Fordered to pay more than #1,500 after
OL,15,Fdefacing the statue by painting
OL,16,F"racist" on its plinth during a
OL,17,Fclimate protest.
OL,26,@xD@AOUxD@HO]
