OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1772460676
OL,3,CMan arrested after Winston Churchill
OL,4,Cstatue daubed with graffiti
OL,6,FThe 12ft-tall monument, created by
OL,7,FIvor Roberts-Jones, was unveiled in
OL,8,F1973 by the former prime minister's
OL,9,Fwife Lady Clementine Churchill.
OL,11,FIt is one of 12 statues on or around
OL,12,FParliament Square, most of well-known
OL,13,Fstatesmen such as Abraham Lincoln and
OL,14,FNelson Mandela.
OL,16,FWestminster City Council have been
OL,17,Fcontacted for comment.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/7
